channel.title: Need Help With Compiling And Run
channel.description:
When I compile I get:
You must have Java files for this Compiler to Compile.
I used Mod Taharok's 'Perfect' Compiler.
When I run server I get:
Exception in thread "main" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: PlayerHandler at server.main(server.java:26) Exception in thread "Thread-0" java.lang.NoClassDefFoundError: misc at server.run(server.java:128) at java.lang.Thread.run(Unknown Source) Press any key to continue . . .
I am using Cheezescape
